so long after the fact.

09:51.909 --> 09:54.454
So let me make this
plain to you.

09:54.495 --> 09:57.165
If the issue involves,
as your patch suggests,

09:57.206 --> 09:59.792
fish and wildlife,

09:59.834 --> 10:02.586
have at it. Otherwise,

10:02.628 --> 10:05.381
stay out of police business.

10:05.423 --> 10:07.800
