14:48.539 --> 14:50.499
How is your sight picture

14:50.541 --> 14:52.960
these days, hmm?

14:58.173 --> 15:01.761
You know, Dad never really
talks about his brother.

15:03.763 --> 15:06.557
Well, it's not an easy thing
for him to discuss.

15:06.599 --> 15:09.143
Believe me, I've tried.

15:09.184 --> 15:12.271
It's what he might call
repression.

15:14.273 --> 15:16.900
Your father's very good
at his job,

15:16.942 --> 15:21.572
but he could stand to point that powerful
psychiatric microscope at himself once in a while.

15:23.907 --> 15:27.286
Do it!

15:27.328 --> 15:30.331
Okay. How did I use
to do this?

15:30.372 --> 15:33.875
I am deeply concerned.

15:33.917 --> 15:35.919
That's good.
