concerned by that.

15:53.521 --> 15:57.024
Ha, ha, ha! You know, it's uh,

15:57.065 --> 15:59.026
it's a good thing I leave
the office from time to time

15:59.067 --> 16:01.153
or I might mistake myself

16:01.195 --> 16:04.365
- for a respected man.
- Yes, honey, it is a very good thing

16:04.406 --> 16:07.702
